      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this 2019 BMW M2 Competition is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast. Finished in Hockenheim Silver Metallic, the exterior is absolutely flawless, having been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating since day one\u2014there are zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections to be found. The factory wheels are pristine, with no curb rash or pitting. The interior remains in a 'time-capsule' state; the Black Dakota leather retains its original matte factory finish with no bolster wear, the carbon fiber trim is vibrant, and the cabin is strictly smoke-free. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history exclusively through BMW authorized centers. Always garaged under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the pinnacle of its class. Included are both original keys, all factory manuals, and a meticulous folder of maintenance records. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been maintained to the highest possible standard.",
